{"tid":216844,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"食左A酸左一年  (有圖)","createTime":"2017-04-25T12:59:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-25T13:18:16.000Z","uid":56534,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7081977436ae50aa0ed5f64b5a188303582037c7","tid":216844,"uid":56534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T12:59:29.000Z","msg":"本身混合性肌膚 <br />\n兩邊面都係暗瘡 <br />\n好在未係月球表面<br />\n但都唔見得人 好唔開心<br />\n成收埋自己 唔出街<br />\n試過做化學換膚 殖針都冇用<br />\n所以試下食a酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食完乾撚到仆街 個嘴就成日龜裂<br />\n而且藥費真係好貴 食到好肉赤<br />\n不過真係最有用<br />\n<br />\n呢張相影個陣係已經食左兩個月<br />\n因為最嚴重個時真係好樣衰<br />\n完全唔想影相<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83ccd3c553018315ad41e59de31930b0b08d1886","tid":216844,"uid":37343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T13:01:05.000Z","msg":"原相呢?無格?"},{"pid":"e36e0c3e489a8f89aacaecebfcdb029ae9bfa426","tid":216844,"uid":25204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T13:01:50.000Z","msg":"第一張又唔係話好嚴重<br />\n唉 搞啲凹凸洞先kick手 好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"171730e167608cd4a890cec38fc9fa8b8e9e810b","tid":216844,"uid":87493,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T13:03:12.000Z","msg":"又釣狗公系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a705354278193fef70f1679bdc045c40deae3b60","tid":216844,"uid":56534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T13:03:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原相呢?無格?</blockquote><br />\n你話未食之前?"},{"pid":"d4e4871c65007fb2d413f9213c3abd2961245952","tid":216844,"uid":73,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T13:05:07.000Z","msg":"你d 瘡生心口太核突要打格?"},{"pid":"5009fba6e8b699b7e4cece1eaa62a0468e816fa4","tid":216844,"uid":56534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T13:05:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一張又唔係話好嚴重<br />\n唉